data.description: Beautifully UPDATED 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage POOL home with large fenced yard! NO HOA, NO CDD - bring your boat/toys/RV! No Flood Zone. NEW HVAC. You are greeted with fresh exterior paint and modern finishes! Upon entering you will notice the new interior paint, new luxury waterproof vinyl flooring, and modern fixtures. Plenty of living space with a formal living room and dining room with pool access thru the French doors. Updated Kitchen with shaker cabinets, Granite counter tops, new stainless steel appliances, subway tile back splash, and bonus eat-in kitchen space. Second family room is open to the kitchen with sliding door access to the screened lanai POOL area - perfect for entertaining! Split bedroom floor plan with new plush carpeting in bedrooms. Spacious Primary's suite with his and her closets and en suite bathroom with updated vanity and shower stall plus bonus access to the pool! Guest bedrooms are spacious and have plenty of closet storage. Four bedrooms gives you the option for a home office or flex space! Hall bathroom has updated vanity and shower/tub combo. Huge fenced backyard is shaded and has a tree swing already in place! This home is fully updated and won't last long!  Close to Bloomingdale area restaurants/shopping, schools, US 301, Crosstown Expwy, and I-75 for commute!
